column7: Maikeru - Japanese Grill and Bar is a Japanese restaurant with a modern izakaya concept that serves authentic - modern Japanese food (No Pork No Lard) such as yakitori, bento and handcraft drinks such as cocktails, mocktails, and also provides draft beer. And also with "Open Kitchen" concept, you can see Chef making products. Maikeru is suitable for lunch and hangout with friends after work or suitable for those who wants to chillax. Maikeru provides a VIP room that is suitab...le for meetings or special events with family and colleagues.  selengkapnya>
